<HEADLINE>  Spain's Anton Wins Marathon </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	SEVILLE, Spain (AP) -- Spain's Abel Anton delighted a home crowd  
at Olympic Stadium Saturday, using his finishing kick over the last 
12 minutes to win his second straight World Championships marathon 
and Spain's second gold. 
