<HEADLINE> Excerpts of Midway Battle Letter </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	Excerpts from the ``Lost Letter of Midway,'' newly discovered  
recollections of Vice Adm. Stanhope Cotton Ring, who wrote in 1946 
about the early hours of the pivotal World War II Battle of Midway, 
June 4-6, 1942: 
</P>
